  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.wdjimg.com/mms/icon/v1/b/7a/1b7ac6f8826971800db4c448dc1637ab_256_256.png\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p763970\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tBut we start in the US where a man has been arrested and charged for plotting an attack on the US Capitol building. Our North America <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/editor\" target=\"_blank\">editor</a> Jon Sopel spoke to me from Washington.</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;We've just got the court documents from the Ohio district court, and it cites an attempted killing of a US government officer and the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/possession\" target=\"_blank\">possession</a> of a firearm in <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/furtherance\" target=\"_blank\">furtherance</a> of an attempted crime of violence. That's on the front cover of the court. It seems that the FBI had been monitoring Christopher Cornell for a little while. He was also known on Twitter as 'Raheel Mahrus Ubaydah' and had wanted to forge an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/alliance\" target=\"_blank\">alliance</a> with Islamic State. It seems that he had been researching how to make pipe bombs and how to source a semi-automatic weapon and how much it would cost. They had been watching him. When he went to buy the weapon, which he did <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/allegedly\" target=\"_blank\">allegedly</a> today an ArmaLite semi-automatic plus 600 rounds of ammunition with a plan to travel to Washington DC and kill employees, and officers working in and around the US Capitol. When I say that I'm reading from the court documents, it was then that the Joint Terrorism Task Force decided that they would move in and they have arrested Cornell and he is now in <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/custody\" target=\"_blank\">custody</a>.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a>英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。&gt;&gt;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/52569?source=16553\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">零基础直达流利生活口语班</a>&lt;&lt;</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p763970/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p763970\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763469/\">看脱口秀学英语：效果=和老外对话！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764319/\">12星座的2016运势解读！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764309/\">美国历史上针对女性的9条奇葩禁令</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764101/\">逗你一笑的趣味漫画：动物一家亲超萌超暖心</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762639/\">从早做起：健康的人早餐吃什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763962/\">只有常看美剧的人才懂的16个表达！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p764333/\">13星座是什么鬼！新加的蛇夫座什么来头？！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763944/\">少女心炸！梦幻到不像话的棉花糖不忍下口！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p763920/\">全国寒潮来袭！被冻懵逼的人才懂的9个事实</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762717/\">男人秃吧不是罪！威廉王子新发型萌网友点赞</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" tar